<Layout title="Natural Resource Conservation – Evamor Africa">

  <h1>Natural Resource Conservation</h1>

  <p>
    Natural resource conservation is central to Evamor Africa’s mission.
    We work to protect ecosystems, promote sustainable resource management,
    and support communities whose livelihoods depend on healthy natural
    environments.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Focus</h2>

  <p>
    Environmental degradation, climate change, and unsustainable land use
    continue to threaten biodiversity and natural ecosystems. Our conservation
    efforts focus on balancing environmental protection with community needs,
    ensuring that natural resources are preserved for future generations.
  </p>

  <h2>What We Do</h2>

  <ul class="content-list">
    <li>Promote sustainable land and water management practices</li>
    <li>Support community-led conservation initiatives</li>
    <li>Raise awareness on biodiversity protection and ecosystem health</li>
    <li>Advocate for policies that safeguard natural resources</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why It Matters</h2>

  <p>
    Conserving natural resources strengthens climate resilience, protects
    livelihoods, and ensures long-term environmental sustainability. Through
    collaborative and locally driven approaches, we aim to create lasting
    impact at both community and ecosystem levels.
  </p>

</Layout>
